74 Years of Wisdom | Dr. LaDonna Osborn
snippet.description:
During the entire month of March we are posting a 3-minute podcast to inspire you and to celebrate my birthday.

Celebrating "74 Years of Wisdom" is an opportunity for us to share my answers to specific questions that have been posed to me. I love to help people find clarity and relevance in the Word of God.

I've been in ministry for over 50 years among people of more than 100 nations, cultures and most religions. Many things have changed in my 7 plus decades, but THE TRUTHS OF Jesus Christ remain the same!
